PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779966178
OL,3,CLoved ones of police officer killed in
OL,4,Cline of duty to take on fundraiser
OL,6,FHis friends, Jamie Simpson and Joe
OL,7,FWorsley, similarly remember Bradley as
OL,8,Fa "one in a million" individual who
OL,9,Fwas a "constant ray of laughter and
OL,10,Fhappiness".
OL,12,FIt's in memory of Bradley that the
OL,13,Ftrio will be taking on the Three Peaks
OL,14,Fchallenge in June and raising funds
OL,15,Ffor the Kent, Surrey and Sussex Air
OL,16,FAmbulance.
OL,18,FBradley was a Kent Police Constable
OL,19,Fwho died last March whilst responding
OL,20,Fto an "immediate call" in Farningham,
OL,21,Fnear Swanley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
