OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779966178
OL,3,CLoved ones of police officer killed in
OL,4,Cline of duty to take on fundraiser
OL,6,FHe was travelling in a marked Ford
OL,7,FFocus police car which collided with a
OL,8,FVolkswagen Scirocco on the westbound
OL,9,FA20 London Road at the junction with
OL,10,FButton Street.
OL,12,FBradley was airlifted to hospital
OL,13,Fwhere he later died.
OL,15,FThe incident left his colleague in a
OL,16,Fcritical condition. He has since been
OL,17,Fdischarged. A member of the public in
OL,18,Fthe second vehicle was also treated
OL,19,Ffor serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
