FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779966178
OL,3,CLoved ones of police officer killed in
OL,4,Cline of duty to take on fundraiser
OL,6,FNathan, Jamie and Joe now want to
OL,7,Frepay the air ambulance, which
OL,8,Fprolonged Bradley's life so that his
OL,9,Floved ones could say goodbye.
OL,11,F"I kept holding his hand and kissed
OL,12,Fhim a thousand times, saying 'you're
OL,13,Fso strong'," said Nathan.
OL,15,FJamie added: "It was the toughest
OL,16,Fthree days of my life, but I'll be
OL,17,Fforever grateful for that moment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
