PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779966178
OL,3,CLoved ones of police officer killed in
OL,4,Cline of duty to take on fundraiser
OL,6,FThey say Bradley's "fighting spirit"
OL,7,Fwill spur them on to climb Ben Nevis,
OL,8,FScafell Pike and Snowden all within 24
OL,9,Fhours.
OL,11,FNathan said: "I just know he'll be
OL,12,Fpushing us all up and celebrating when
OL,13,Fwe get to the final one."
OL,15,FIt's a sentiment shared by Joe, who
OL,16,Fexplained: "It doesn't feel like we're
OL,17,Fdoing it on behalf of him. It really
OL,18,Ffeels like the four of us are going to
OL,19,Fbe going there."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
